            "title": "英超｜阿仙奴18歲小將24場2紅4黃 阿迪達警告：學習守紀律",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f9a09ed310f90ce290c89e4f103ce81c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250308/_2025030811040994828.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>阿仙奴的18歲左閘路易斯史基利表現出色於今季彈起，然而場上不時魯莽犯規，今季已兩度直紅被逐，領隊阿迪達直言這會拖累球隊，警告這位年輕人要學習守紀律。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/89c513dc87beefad6be0582ee610da15/2025-03/2025-02-15T131535Z_227788797_UP1EL2F10TY65_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-LEI-ARS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利(黑衫)。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e82d01d19cc5ed79a257defdcfbac2b8/2025-03/2025-03-04T215459Z_1453023010_UP1EL341KWXOI_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-PSV-ARS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利(黑衫)。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5573e99a9877beeeb71bdce6f5f82b57/2025-03/2025-02-22T163327Z_879219176_UP1EL2M19ZQO7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-ARS-WHU-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a7540de78b37d662690a56711e2be030/2025-03/2025-02-22T163308Z_617150085_UP1EL2M19Z7O2_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-ARS-WHU-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2edbd7ba30c95fbd5bcb47daaa00c32/2025-03/2025-02-22T163223Z_18058266_UP1EL2M19XYNY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-ARS-WHU-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4bfde51edc68063601a82ddf0618a5d/2025-03/2025-01-25T154750Z_341921978_UP1EL1P17VPX0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-WOL-ARS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43903e93866a432522be2c7e92da5453/2025-03/2025-01-25T154712Z_1569791789_UP1EL1P17UMWW_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-WOL-ARS-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴小將路易斯史基利今季兩度直紅。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>史基利兩度被逐</h2>\n<p>由於阿仙奴季初後防人手緊拙，令18歲的年青左閘路易斯史基利獲得上位機會，如今更坐穩正選。然而，此子場上紀律為人詬病，今季各賽事上陣24場已經兩度直接領紅出場，雖然其中一張事後獲推翻，但同時也4次領黃牌，包括上場歐聯對燕豪芬只踢了24分鐘就領黃，令阿迪達只好於35分鐘就提早換走他。\n\n</p><h2>遭阿迪達警告</h2>\n<p>阿迪達周五出席英超對曼聯的賽前記者會時直言：「上場他很早領黃，會成為後防的弱點，我不想冒險所以換走他，希望他會上一課。我們都會支持和幫助他，但體育世界犯規的界線真的很模糊，希望他會明白。」阿迪達續指此子要提高防守水平避免紀律問題：「他需要控制好他的防守空間。在攔截時要衡量有多少機率可搶到皮球。」<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2056977/即時-體育-英超-阿仙奴18歲小將24場2紅4黃-阿迪達警告-學習守紀律",
