            "title": "尖沙咀保時捷失控毀兩米鐵欄  司機有驚無險",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"保時捷失控撞欄。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f9500488c665f8b80794581cf5dd0ee9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250308/_2025030811281873202.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">保時捷失控撞欄。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（8日）晨10時24分，一輛紅色電動保時捷沿梳士巴利道往尖沙咀碼頭方向行駛，馳至文化中心對開時，保時捷失控撞毀右邊兩米鐵欄，保時捷車頭損毁，氣袋彈出，事件中無人受傷。據了解，男司機報稱駕駛時車廂內有物品打翻，引致注意力分散釀意外。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125592/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"保時捷失控撞欄。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f77b42e4433e81af8fe2500563478d97/2025-03/02_1_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保時捷失控撞欄。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4125593/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"保時捷失控撞欄。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68be7178cdc76b373cc4f15d74ef86a2/2025-03/03_0_4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n     